{"tid":1507990,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"點解中國動漫質素會咁差？","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T09:27:49.000Z","uid":310266,"like":12,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"5339296a53cd17f378795236da8e87ca2234cff9","tid":1507990,"uid":310266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"如題，點解呢？華漫水平可以低成這樣，我相信冇一個香港人會對嗰啲爛片有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，難聽啲講係垃圾。如果你有㩒過入去睇華漫，絕對有機會令你感到人生絕望。不過作為動漫迷，我都係要研究唔同類型嘅acg。以下我會講下點解啲華漫咁劣。(動畫為主)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1</span>. <strong>中國的動畫不是動畫</strong><br />\n有睇過會知，佢哋動畫係畫到真人風，做嘅動作有延遲，即使更近乎人樣，其生硬嘅人物破壞哂成套動畫。而且違背咗一個好重要嘅原則，真嘅好假，假嘅好真。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">2</span>.<strong>動畫題材</strong><br />\n相比日本，大陸啲題材可以話係冇。所謂題材，只是要在不同處境，不同年齡。以日本動畫為例，好多都是以異世界、校園等背景，而絕大多數的角色都是處於初中到大學的年紀。透過角色性格，劇情發展造成了一部部新鮮嘅作品，但係大陸嘅題材就係可塑性上差得多。題材圍繞愛情(韓劇式)，英雄類，及後的劇情都是直線發展。 當故事內容接近的題材已經泛濫，之後的動畫也不會再好看。"},{"pid":"8c90800ba55b917ae90dc17f05b4c21fcea1b9f5","tid":1507990,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"[9．1機場] 文宣集合 2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507880</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=45977c3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe</a>"},{"pid":"6cad861046f4c92cc69eea57b5316e62662615aa","tid":1507990,"uid":76680,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"首先中國人質素差"},{"pid":"6a7725762fc26015e92df7bf37acc7391f6c74fc","tid":1507990,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"中華拳王"},{"pid":"d26c5adfcc404dcd0f0d3999be92126ea93a61ed","tid":1507990,"uid":35560,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"睇過幾套大陸漫<br />\n完全無劇情可言，佢想點寫就點寫<br />\n一集得10頁 但得幾句對白 <br />\n講完等於無講"},{"pid":"5c95b17f199f51e7c5b3c9ffc18c16f2cde6a28d","tid":1507990,"uid":310266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"大家點睇，一陣再寫，宜家食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165d2ace20577ccc9c21ccb9f3f9bd63d5a9258f","tid":1507990,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=6fe0c5f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=06e0905e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=f1e07d9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"da8f7605a8eea8db0971cb755e022c10a9d82de0","tid":1507990,"uid":74012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"畫風老土"},{"pid":"66f4b1573bd7506f5dcb7647d94a659f77c3d3b6","tid":1507990,"uid":134012,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"<